data.description: This beautiful getaway is minutes from town. Enjoy over 22 acres of privacy. Deer blinds, walking and offroad vehicle trail onsite. Retire to the main house or casita. Plenty of outdoor space for entertaining. Crown molding throughout, Wood cabinets, dual sinks in primary his & hers walk in closets, stained floors for easy maintenance. Full laundry room.  The Primary suite is conveniently on the opposite side of home with its own private patio. 2nd and 3rd bedrooms are perfectly located across living room for privacy. This lovely home has solar panels, more than enough covered parking and several outdoor areas. The casita, just off the main home has a sitting, kitchen and bedroom for guests. Two man made lakes just need to be finished out.  Property is fenced and has an electric gate for entry. Corner Lot, creek bed. A must see!! Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity.
